  <h3>Pointer</h3>
  <p>
    Headings are not interactive elements and therefore have no pointer
    interaction.
  </p>
  <p>
    A heading may give the illusion of being an interactive element if it
    contains a link, or is wrapped in a link, but the heading element itself is
    not clickable.
  </p>
